xie x7r5mf7 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft" data-testid="cell-frame-primary-detail"><span class="x140p0ai x1gufx9m x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1lliihq x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px; --x-8dd7yt: -0.0137em; --x-hxtmnb: 0.0137em;">Sunday</span></div></div><div class="x6s0dn4 xhslqc4 x78zum5 x1nxh6w3 x1fc57z9 xr9ek0c xisnujt" data-testid="cell-frame-secondary"><div class="xjbqb8w x1iyjqo2 x1f6kntn x1fc57z9 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1yc453h xlyipyv xuxw1ft xo1l8bm"><span class="x78zum5 x1cy8zhl" title="‪---

Project Title

LuxeSpace Interior Design Management System (LIDMS)


---

Project Description

Project Overview

LuxeSpace Interior Design Management System (LIDMS) is a comprehensive cloud-based web application designed to digitize and streamline the operations of a modern interior design company. The platform serves as an integrated solution for managing clients, interior design projects, staff, contractors, suppliers, materials, quotations, invoices, payments, and project documentation from a single centralized system.

The system is developed specifically for companies offering residential, commercial, hospitality, institutional, and government interior design services. Whether designing luxury homes, apartments, villas, offices, hotels, restaurants, hospitals, schools, churches, retail stores, or government facilities, the platform enables the company to efficiently plan, execute, monitor, and deliver projects while maintaining high standards of professionalism and customer satisfaction.

Unlike a traditional business website that only advertises services, LIDMS functions as a complete Interior Design Management System. Clients can browse the company&#39;s portfolio, request consultations, submit project requirements, upload inspiration images, receive quotations, approve designs, monitor project progress, communicate with designers, make secure online payments through M-Pesa, and automatically receive KRA eTIMS-compliant electronic invoices and receipts.

Internally, the platform enables management to assign projects to designers, site supervisors, and contractors, monitor project timelines and milestones, coordinate supplier deliveries, manage material procurement, oversee installations, track budgets and project costs, and maintain all project-related documents in one secure location. Automated notifications keep both clients and staff informed about appointments, quotation approvals, payment confirmations, material deliveries, project updates, and important deadlines.

To enhance creativity and improve decision-making, the platform incorporates Artificial Intelligence (AI) features that assist designers and clients by generating room visualization previews, recommending furniture arrangements, suggesting colour palettes and interior styles, estimating project costs, and providing intelligent material recommendations based on project requirements and client preferences.

The system also integrates comprehensive reporting and analytics that provide insights into project performance, sales, revenue, material utilization, supplier performance, and customer satisfaction, enabling management to make informed business decisions and improve operational efficiency.

By integrating client management, project management, procurement, supplier coordination, financial workflows, AI-assisted design tools, M-Pesa payments, and KRA eTIMS compliance into one secure platform, the LuxeSpace Interior Design Management System provides an end-to-end digital solution that improves productivity, enhances customer experience, ensures regulatory compliance, and positions the company to successfully undertake private, commercial, and government interior design projects.


---

Vision

To become one of Africa&#39;s leading technology-driven interior design companies by delivering innovative, sustainable, and customer-focused interior solutions supported by modern digital technologies.


---

Mission

To transform interior spaces into functional, elegant, and inspiring environments while leveraging technology to improve project management, client collaboration, operational efficiency, and service delivery.


---

Business Scope

The company provides professional interior design services for:

Residential Projects

Luxury Homes

Apartments

Villas

Bungalows

Bedrooms

Living Rooms

Kitchens

Bathrooms

Dining Rooms

Home Offices

Outdoor Living Spaces


Commercial &amp; Institutional Projects

Hotels

Resorts

Restaurants

Cafés

Office Buildings

Banks

Shopping Malls

Retail Stores

Supermarkets

Hospitals

Clinics

Schools

Universities

Churches

Conference Centres

Government Offices

Salons

Reception Areas

Co-working Spaces



---

Professional Services

The company offers comprehensive interior design solutions including:

Interior Design Consultation

Site Visits and Space Measurement

Space Planning

Interior Architecture

Concept Design

Mood Board Development

2D Floor Plans

3D Interior Visualization

Virtual Design Walkthroughs

Furniture Selection

Custom Furniture and Cabinet Design

Kitchen and Wardrobe Design

Ceiling Design

Lighting Design

Flooring Design

Wall Finishes and Decorative Panels

Paint and Colour Consultation

Curtain and Blind Design

Interior Decoration and Styling

Renovation and Remodeling

Material Procurement

Supplier Coordination

Project Supervision

Installation Services

Landscaping and Outdoor Design

Smart Home Interior Integration



---

System Modules

The platform consists of integrated modules that support the company&#39;s daily operations:

Client Management

Manage customer profiles, enquiries, consultation requests, project history, communication, and feedback.

Project Management

Create and manage projects, assign designers and contractors, monitor milestones, timelines, budgets, and project progress.

Interior Design Studio

Develop mood boards, colour palettes, furniture layouts, 2D floor plans, 3D visualizations, and AI-assisted design concepts.

Staff &amp; Contractor Management

Assign tasks to designers, site supervisors, and contractors, monitor progress, manage schedules, and track work completion.

Procurement &amp; Supplier Management

Manage suppliers, purchase orders, material requests, deliveries, inventory levels, and procurement records.

Quotation &amp; Financial Management

Generate quotations, estimates, invoices, receipts, project budgets, payment records, and financial reports.

Portfolio Management

Showcase completed projects with high-quality images, videos, testimonials, and before-and-after transformations.

Document Management

Securely manage contracts, floor plans, CAD drawings, project images, invoices, quotations, warranties, and project documents.

Analytics Dashboard

Monitor project performance, revenue, project costs, customer satisfaction, procurement activities, and overall business performance.


---

Key Features

The system provides powerful features that simplify the company&#39;s operations, including:

Client registration and secure login

Online consultation booking

Project request submission

Project progress tracking

2D and 3D design previews

AI-powered room visualization

AI design recommendations

Digital mood boards

Task assignment and staff coordination

Contractor management

Supplier management

Material inventory tracking

Automated quotation generation

Invoice generation

Automatic KRA eTIMS tax invoice generation

Automatic electronic receipt generation

Secure M-Pesa payment integration

Real-time payment verification

Email and SMS notifications

In-app notifications

Project milestone alerts

Appointment reminders

Client design approval workflow

Secure file uploads and document storage

Business reports and analytics



---

Third-Party Integrations

The system integrates with essential external services to enhance efficiency and compliance:

KRA eTIMS – Automatic generation and submission of electronic tax invoices and receipts.

Safaricom M-Pesa – Secure mobile payments through STK Push, PayBill, and Till Number integration.

Email Services – Delivery of quotations, invoices, receipts, contracts, and project updates.

SMS Gateway – Appointment reminders, payment confirmations, project notifications, and delivery alerts.

Google Maps – Site visit locations and project mapping.

Cloud Storage – Secure storage of design files, contracts, images, videos, and project documentation.



---

Expected Benefits

The LuxeSpace Interior Design Management System will:

Digitize the company&#39;s entire interior design workflow.

Improve collaboration between clients, designers, contractors, and suppliers.

Simplify project planning and execution.

Automate quotations, invoices, and receipt generation.

Ensure compliance with KRA eTIMS requirements.

Enable secure online payments through M-Pesa.

Improve communication through automated notifications.

Enhance project transparency with real-time progress tracking.

Reduce paperwork and manual record-keeping.

Improve procurement and material management.

Strengthen customer satisfaction through a professional client portal.

Provide business insights through comprehensive analytics.

Enable the company to efficiently manage residential, commercial, and government interior design projects.



---

Overall Goal

The primary goal of the LuxeSpace Interior Design Management System (LIDMS) is to provide an intelligent, secure, and centralized digital platform that simplifies the management of interior design projects from consultation to project handover. By integrating client relationship management, project planning, staff and contractor coordination, procurement, AI-assisted design, M-Pesa payment processing, and KRA eTIMS-compliant invoicing into one platform, the system will improve operational efficiency, enhance customer experience, and support the company&#39;s growth as a competitive interior design firm capable of delivering high-quality residential, commercial, and government projects.‬" data-testid="last-msg-status"><span>Reacted <img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="👍🏿" draggable="false" class="x1k0y4fr b38 emoji wa  xnpuxes" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: 0px -60px;"> to:</span><span>&nbsp;</span>"<span dir="ltr" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu xnpuxes" style="min-height: 0px;">---

