" data-pre-plain-text="[00:34, 7/21/2026] Rocky carter: "><div class="x1n2onr6 x1mzt3pk x126k92a x6ikm8r x10wlt62"><span data-testid="selectable-text" dir="ltr" class="x1f6kntn xjb2p0i x8r4c90 xo1l8bm x1ic7a3i x12xpedu xnpuxes selectable-text copyable-text" style="min-height: 0px;"><span class="x1lliihq">Use this prompt:
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq"><blockquote dir="ltr" class="x1rg5ohu x1n2onr6 xh8yej3 xhslqc4 xav9cv8 x4tpdpg xnpuxes selectable-text copyable-text" data-testid="selectable-text" data-pre-plain-text="&gt; "><div class="x10l6tqk x1o0tod x13vifvy x5yr21d x1g8rjiy x1518k6t xkqq1k2 x91jh78 x1xkn691 x4oqio7"></div><div class="x1rg5ohu x1gx403c xj0a0fe xeaf4i8">Fix the navigation and resume download across the entire portfolio.
</div></blockquote></span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The main problem is that on mobile the header links are missing, and the links like Home, About, Case Studies/Work, Contact are only visible in the footer. That is not acceptable.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Navigation Fix
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Make the header visible on every page on both mobile and desktop
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The header must include:
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Home
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">About
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Case Studies / Work
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Resume
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Contact
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Keep the header sticky at the top
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">On mobile, use a clean hamburger menu or compact responsive nav, but the links must still be easy to access
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The header should never disappear on scroll unless intentionally collapsed into a mobile menu
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Keep the footer links too, but the header must be the primary navigation
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="">Make the same navigation a…</span></span> <div role="button" tabindex="0" data-testid="caption-read-more-button" class="xuxw1ft x1ypdohk x1rg5ohu xo1mcw5 x1xlr1w8 x1hl2dhg xt0b8zv xbvygy2 x17f7hit xp30eni xhmieyt read-more-button">Read more</div><span class=""><span class="x3nfvp2 xxymvpz xlshs6z xqtp20y xexx8yu x1uc92m x18d9i69 x181vq82 x12lo8hy x152skdk" aria-hidden="true"><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xn6xy2s"></span><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s">00:34</span></span></span></div></div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1n327nk x18mqm2i xhsvlbd x14z9mp xz62fqu x1wbi8v6"><div class="x1bvqhpb xx3o462 xuxw1ft x78zum5 x6s0dn4 x12lo8hy x152skdk" data-testid="msg-meta" role="button"><span class="x1rg5ohu x16dsc37" dir="auto"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px;">00:34</span></span><div class="xhslqc4 x1rg5ohu x7phf20"><span aria-hidden="false" aria-label=" Read " class="x1rv0e52"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" class="" fill="currentColor"><title>wds-ic-read</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M14.73 6.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15l.01.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41L7.6 18.01a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05c-.26 0-.52-.11-.71-.3l-4.03-4.09a.99.99 0 0 1 0-1.41.99.99 0 0 1 1.41 0l3.25 3.29 7.99-9.86Zm5.71.12a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15h-.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41l-8.41 10.45a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05a1 1 0 0 1-.71-.3l-1.36-1.26a.55.55 0 0 1-.02-.81l.56-.68c.21-.2.53-.21.75-.03l.71.58 7.71-9.58Z"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></div></div><span class=""></span><div class="x10l6tqk xyc4j8s xceh6e4"></div></div></div><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 x78zum5 xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xeuugli x2lwn1j x13a6bvl x1q0g3np x6s0dn4 xken49m xexx8yu x18d9i69 x135b78x x11lfxj5 x10l6tqk xwa60dl xfvs6mw xho9bl7"><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 xeuugli x2lwn1j xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xexx8yu x1im30kd x18d9i69 x1djpfga xcxita6"><div></div></div></div></div><div class="x78zum5 xbfrwjf x8k05lb xeq5yr9 x1n2onr6 x1f889gz xpvyfi4" data-testid="addon-bubble-container"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div tabindex="-1" class="" role="row"><div tabindex="-1" class="x1n2onr6 xa0aww2" data-id="ACA1F1BDA0F43AB87C52A38DB18F95A7" data-testid="conv-msg-ACA1F1BDA0F43AB87C52A38DB18F95A7"><div class="x78zum5 xdt5ytf" data-virtualized="false"><div class=""><div class="x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1hx0egp x1wxbj4f xds8fti xh1vicy x1rzuvji xuk3077 focusable-list-item x1klvx2g xahtqtb"><span class=""></span><div data-testid="msg-container" class="x1liijdw xu342n7 xelbjmh x16pgt24 x14ug900 x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xdl72j9 x12lqup9 x17fgdl5 x1n2onr6 x1qg1ob xxx6ivz x1gx27l9 x14fraq8 x2nxwck xb3dwbw"><div class="x1liijdw xu342n7 xelbjmh x16pgt24 x1n2onr6 x12xzxwr x1g5lz36 xgdw1sx false false"><div><div><div class="x9f619 x1hx0egp x1yrsyyn xodvfiu xct3hqd xwib8y2"><div class="copyable-text" data-pre-plain-text="[09:38, 7/21/2026] Rocky carter: "><div class="x1n2onr6 x1mzt3pk x126k92a x6ikm8r x10wlt62"><span data-testid="selectable-text" dir="ltr" class="x1f6kntn xjb2p0i x8r4c90 xo1l8bm x1ic7a3i x12xpedu xnpuxes selectable-text copyable-text" style="min-height: 0px;"><span class="x1lliihq">Here's an improved version of your prompt with the additional requirements incorporated:
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">---
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Portfolio Navigation, Resume &amp; Content Enhancement
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Fix the navigation, resume functionality, and portfolio content across the entire website.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Navigation Fix
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The biggest issue is that on mobile devices the header navigation is missing. The links such as Home, About, Case Studies (Work), Resume, and Contact only appear in the footer, which creates a poor user experience.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Requirements:
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Make the header visible on every page on both desktop and mobile.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The header must always contain:
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Home
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">About
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Case Studies / Work
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Resume
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Contact
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Keep the header sticky at the top.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="">On mobile, implement a modern hamburger menu with smooth open/close animations while keeping …</span></span> <div role="button" tabindex="0" data-testid="caption-read-more-button" class="xuxw1ft x1ypdohk x1rg5ohu xo1mcw5 x1xlr1w8 x1hl2dhg xt0b8zv xbvygy2 x17f7hit xp30eni xhmieyt read-more-button">Read more</div><span class=""><span class="x3nfvp2 xxymvpz xlshs6z xqtp20y xexx8yu x1uc92m x18d9i69 x181vq82 x12lo8hy x152skdk" aria-hidden="true"><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xn6xy2s"></span><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s">09:38</span></span></span></div></div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1n327nk x18mqm2i xhsvlbd x14z9mp xz62fqu x1wbi8v6"><div class="x1bvqhpb xx3o462 xuxw1ft x78zum5 x6s0dn4 x12lo8hy x152skdk" data-testid="msg-meta" role="button"><span class="x1rg5ohu x16dsc37" dir="auto"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px;">09:38</span></span><div class="xhslqc4 x1rg5ohu x7phf20"><span aria-hidden="false" aria-label=" Read " class="x1rv0e52"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" class="" fill="currentColor"><title>wds-ic-read</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M14.73 6.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15l.01.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41L7.6 18.01a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05c-.26 0-.52-.11-.71-.3l-4.03-4.09a.99.99 0 0 1 0-1.41.99.99 0 0 1 1.41 0l3.25 3.29 7.99-9.86Zm5.71.12a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15h-.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41l-8.41 10.45a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05a1 1 0 0 1-.71-.3l-1.36-1.26a.55.55 0 0 1-.02-.81l.56-.68c.21-.2.53-.21.75-.03l.71.58 7.71-9.58Z"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></div></div><span class=""></span><div class="x10l6tqk xyc4j8s xceh6e4"></div></div></div><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 x78zum5 xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xeuugli x2lwn1j x13a6bvl x1q0g3np x6s0dn4 xken49m xexx8yu x18d9i69 x135b78x x11lfxj5 x10l6tqk xwa60dl xfvs6mw xho9bl7"><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 xe